{"tid":1274530,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"終於知道點解要玩空城計拖到12點先清場！！！","createTime":"2019-07-01T16:49:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-01T16:54:08.000Z","uid":67294,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8ad478c9a1cf79082dc1e5953e0d4bb99445524c","tid":1274530,"uid":67294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T16:49:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%85%B1%E4%BA%A7%E5%85%9A%E8%AF%9E%E7%94%9F%E7%BA%AA%E5%BF%B5%E6%97%A5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259B%25BD%25E5%2585%25B1%25E4%25BA%25A7%25E5%2585%259A%25E8%25AF%259E%25E7%2594%259F%25E7%25BA%25AA%25E5%25BF%25B5%25E6%2597%25A5&d=qB%2BEr1lTQcBPVU2CyFsNopbpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=ba11dbdb\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%85%B1%E4%BA%A7%E5%85%9A%E8%AF%9E%E7%94%9F%E7%BA%AA%E5%BF%B5%E6%97%A5</a><br />\n中國共產黨誕生紀念日，又稱建黨節、中國共產黨建黨日、中國共產黨建黨紀念日、七一建黨節、黨的生日等，是為紀念中國共產黨於1921年7月成立而設立的紀念日，<strong>1941年中共中央正式將慶祝日期定為每年的7月1日</strong>。中華人民共和國成立後，該紀念日成為一個全國性節日，但不是法定節日。<br />\n<br />\n原來今日係中共生日，應該唔敢係中共生日玩到流血見紅，所以拖到過左12點先黎料<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3e26badc9c362e5385c0e969e2e57b10d725cfa","tid":1274530,"uid":235174,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T16:54:08.000Z","msg":"梁烈士死忌撞正習總生忌"}]}